<li><a href="http://lizhobman.wordpress.com/2011/09/23/power-to-the-students/">Power to the students.</a> (lizhobman.wordpress.com)</li>
<li><a href="http://21stcenturylearningassociates.wordpress.com/2011/09/21/creating-creators-the-role-of-public-education-in-the-21st-century/">Creating Creators: The Role of Public Education in the 21st Century</a> (21stcenturylearningassociates.wordpress.com)</li>
</ul>
</fieldset>
