	<article id="post-204" class="post-204 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-education-and-ict category-learning-2 category-networks-of-the-future category-research tag-book tag-education tag-innovation tag-knowledge tag-learning tag-research-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blogs.oii.ox.ac.uk/cobo/?p=204" rel="bookmark">Invisible Learning released</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://blogs.oii.ox.ac.uk/cobo/?p=204" title="3:49 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-05-05T15:49:23+00:00">05/05/2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blogs.oii.ox.ac.uk/cobo/?author=2" title="View all posts by Cristobal Cobo" rel="author">Cristobal Cobo</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://blogs.oii.ox.ac.uk/cobo/?p=204#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Cristóbal Cobo and I are pleased to announce that the Spanish edition of our new book, <a href="http://www.invisiblelearning.com/en/" target="_blank">Invisible Learning (Aprendizaje Invisible)</a>, has just been released by the University of Barcelona (Col·lecció Transmedia XXI. Laboratori de Mitjans Interactius / Publicacions i Edicions de la Universitat de Barcelona). The e-book is <a href="http://futr.es/libro" target="_blank">available for purchase at the UB website</a> today. The print edition will arrive in the coming months.</p>
<div>*This is a cross-post, published by <a href="http://www.educationfutures.com/2011/04/28/invisible-learning-released/" target="_blank">John Moravec in Education Futures</a>, who is co-author of this book.</div>
<div><a href="http://www.invisiblelearning.com/en/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" title="Invisible Learning - book cover" src="http://www.educationfutures.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/IL_cover-210x300.png" alt="" width="210" height="300" /></a></div>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
